data.description: Discover the sleek modernity of Steel Creek with this pristine 4-bedroom home in the Coventry community, recently enhanced with a fresh coat of paint throughout. The entire home is adorned with durable LVP flooring, setting a welcoming tone from the moment you step inside. The living room, warm and inviting with its fireplace, flows into a  kitchen boasting a center island, cozy breakfast nook, and sophisticated granite countertops. Venture upstairs to find a multi-use loft, a spacious master suite equipped with in-bathroom speakers, and additional bedrooms ideal for family or guests. The exterior features a private deck and a verdant tree line for an oasis of privacy. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and entertainment options, and merely minutes from Carowinds, Rivergate shopping center, Lake Wylie, and a quick 15-minute drive to Uptown Charlotte and the airport. Don't miss your chance to make this beautifully updated sanctuary your new home. Schedule a viewing today!
